Welcome to "aim_hws_texture_arcada_01"

Map created By El_Mexicano


This is an "AIM" map , with 20 slots in each team, 20 slots for the terrorists & 20 
slots for the counter-terroristes!
Which means that there is no aim , the only aim is to kill all players of the other team!
It's a "FUN" map , that's why all the creation of this map was based on the FUN side 
of the map , and that's why i've used the grey & orange textures like the ones you 
can find in "fy_blazin" or " texture_city " map (for those who know them)
There is a hidden WARPZONE , which takes you to a secret room with many coridor and teleport doors & when you'll take the last teleport you'll be in a tube and make a wipeout of 15 seconds with sounds effects & lights effetcs, AWESOME !!!!!!

The .BSP file makes 17,5 MO, the .NAV file makes 0,4 MO ;& the SOUND file makes 0,3 MO
